{"id":930,"parent_id":926,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":930,"title":"Micah 4","subtitle":"","short_title":"Micah","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 4"],[".studySummary",["i","In the last days, the temple will be built, Israel will gather to it, the millennial era will commence, and the Lord will reign in Zion."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.1","order":"02.34.004.61950"},["b","1"],"But in the last days it shall come to pass,",["i","that"],"the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"mountain"],"of the house of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"established"],"in the top of the mountains, and it shall be exalted above the hills; and people shall flow unto it."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.2","order":"02.34.004.61951"},["b","2"],"And many nations shall come, and say, Come, and let us go up to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"mountain"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and to the house of the God of Jacob; and he will teach us of his ways, and we will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"walk"],"in his paths: for the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"law"],"shall go forth of",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_2d"},"Zion"],", and the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"from",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_2e"},"Jerusalem"],"."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.3","order":"02.34.004.61952"},["b","3"],"¶And he shall judge among many people, and rebuke strong nations afar off; and they shall beat their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"swords"],"into plowshares, and their spears into pruninghooks: nation shall not lift up a sword against nation, neither shall they learn",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"war"],"any more."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.4","order":"02.34.004.61953"},["b","4"],"But they shall sit every man under his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"vine"],"and under his fig tree; and none shall make",["i","them"],"afraid: for the mouth of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts hath spoken",["i","it."]],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.5","order":"02.34.004.61954"},["b","5"],"For all people will walk every one in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"name"],"of his god, and we will walk in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"name"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"our God for ever and ever."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.6","order":"02.34.004.61955"},["b","6"],"In that day, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", will I assemble her that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"halteth"],", and I will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"gather"],"her that is driven out, and her that I have afflicted;"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.7","order":"02.34.004.61956"},["b","7"],"And I will make her that halted a remnant, and her that was cast far off a strong nation: and the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"reign"],"over them in mount",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"Zion"],"from henceforth, even for ever."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.8","order":"02.34.004.61957"},["b","8"],"¶And thou, O tower of the flock, the strong hold of the daughter of Zion, unto thee shall it come, even the first dominion; the kingdom shall come to the daughter of Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.9","order":"02.34.004.61958"},["b","9"],"Now why dost thou cry out aloud?",["i","is there"],"no king in thee? is thy counsellor perished? for pangs have taken thee as a woman in travail."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.10","order":"02.34.004.61959"},["b","10"],"Be in pain, and labour to bring forth, O daughter of Zion, like a woman in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"travail"],": for now shalt thou go forth out of the city, and thou shalt dwell in the field, and thou shalt go",["i","even"],"to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"Babylon"],"; there shalt thou be delivered; there the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall redeem thee from the hand of thine",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"enemies"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.11","order":"02.34.004.61960"},["b","11"],"¶Now also many nations are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"gathered"],"against thee, that say, Let her be defiled, and let our eye look upon Zion."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.12","order":"02.34.004.61961"},["b","12"],"But they know not the thoughts of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", neither understand they his counsel: for he shall gather them as the sheaves into the floor."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.13","order":"02.34.004.61962"},["b","13"],"Arise and thresh, O daughter of Zion: for I will make thine horn iron, and I will make thy hoofs brass: and thou shalt",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"beat"],"in pieces many people: and I will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"consecrate"],"their gain unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and their substance unto the Lord of the whole earth."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.1a","order":"02.34.004.61963"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/2.2.1-3"},"Isa. 2:2 (1–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.1b","order":"02.34.004.61965"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/dispensations"},"TG Dispensations"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.2a","order":"02.34.004.61967"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zion"},"TG Zion"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.2b","order":"02.34.004.61969"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-with-god"},"TG Walking with God"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.2c","order":"02.34.004.61971"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.13"},"D&C 58:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"2d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.2d","order":"02.34.004.61973"},["b","2d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jerusalem-new"},"TG Jerusalem, New"],"."],["div",{"id":"2e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.2e","order":"02.34.004.61975"},["b","2e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jerusalem"},"TG Jerusalem"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.3a","order":"02.34.004.61977"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/millennium"},"TG Millennium"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.3b","order":"02.34.004.61979"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/war"},"TG War"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.4a","order":"02.34.004.61981"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/4.25"},"1 Kgs. 4:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.5a","order":"02.34.004.61983"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/134.7.4,7"},"D&C 134:7 (4, 7)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/a-of-f/1.11"},"A of F 1:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.5b","order":"02.34.004.61985"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.12"},"Zech. 10:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.6a","order":"02.34.004.61987"},["b","6a"],["span.small","HEB"],"is lame."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.6b","order":"02.34.004.61989"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-gathering-of"},"TG Israel, Gathering of"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.7a","order":"02.34.004.61991"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/1.33.30-33"},"Luke 1:33 (30–33)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.36"},"D&C 1:36"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/a-of-f/1.10"},"A of F 1:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.7b","order":"02.34.004.61993"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zion"},"TG Zion"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.10a","order":"02.34.004.61995"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.7.7-8"},"Isa. 66:7 (7–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.10b","order":"02.34.004.61997"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/1.13"},"1 Ne. 1:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/omni/1.15"},"Omni 1:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.10c","order":"02.34.004.61999"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/17.10"},"1 Chr. 17:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/89.10"},"Ps. 89:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/65.6"},"D&C 65:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.11a","order":"02.34.004.62001"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.2.1-2,9-14"},"Joel 3:2 (1–2, 9–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/12.3.2-3"},"Zech. 12:3 (2–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.13a","order":"02.34.004.62003"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/20.19.17-22"},"3 Ne. 20:19 (17–22)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.13b","order":"02.34.004.62005"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/2.2"},"2 Ne. 2:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/32.9"},"32:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.30"},"D&C 42:30"],"."]]}
